{"type":"answer","id":261336,"parentType":"question","parentId":25066,"uid":9304,"contents":"见识一下肖博士论自由。将来可能被选为五毛培训班教材。<br>\n可以替《肖博士论自由》做个诠释：手被捆起来不算不自由，心里放不下挣脱的念头才是不自由；嘴巴被封住不算不自由，控制不住自己说话的冲动才是不自由；不能批评党和国家领导人不算不自由，不能撒泼打滚无法无天才是不自由。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQrXUAA4fRT?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQrXUAA4fRT?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQrXUAA4fRT?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQsWwAUonG9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQsWwAUonG9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQsWwAUonG9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQvWwAYn5Ao?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQvWwAYn5Ao?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8q1hQvWwAYn5Ao?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-05-10","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":4}